{"tid":766230,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度可以領養貓但唔洗家訪","createTime":"2018-08-03T12:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T19:10:29.000Z","uid":116018,"like":12,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e591d903ee342423ccf6077952f42eb281192f08","tid":766230,"uid":116018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"住緊公屋，想養貓，屋企人都贊成。<br />\n唔想去愛協領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係喺貓義工度領養貓都要家訪。<br />\n問題黎啦，屋企人唔想俾陌生人上黎屋企，好似查家宅咁。<br />\n如果貓義工擔心環境唔好或窗網問題，我可以影相俾佢睇。<br />\n想問下有無ching領養貓個陣唔洗家訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者分享下家訪個陣嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db53d318ec763af14763c6e92603806436083d55","tid":766230,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa471ef972a84a834826422fd1e0d5d642e4e44","tid":766230,"uid":52942,"like":26,"dislike":29,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"少少錢，買啦，唔好助長d義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1cb9d9cc5f86667dd9ef6589e9c0249e518442","tid":766230,"uid":11420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"問個村屋朋友借間屋用一用 最好有養貓"},{"pid":"4d076f92810a8341642bb955943ded0f57fa4731","tid":766230,"uid":116018,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"eaa471ef972a84a834826422fd1e0d5d642e4e44","tid":766230,"uid":52942,"like":26,"dislike":29,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"少少錢，買啦，唔好助長d義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"買咪助長啲黑心商人，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":